                    test55 History file
                    --------------------
This file should be used by the G4 example coordinator to briefly
summarize all major modifications introduced in the code and keep
track of all tags.

     ----------------------------------------------------------
     * Reverse chronological order (last date on top), please *
     ----------------------------------------------------------

24-04-09  A.Lechner (test55-V09-02-01)
- Added scoring functionality for the mean energy loss of primaries
  transmitted through a material layer. Affected classes are:
   SteppingAction, RunAction 
- Added functionality to compare range and energy loss of primaries
  against reference values (specified in macro file). New classes are
   Test, TestSeries, RunActionMessenger     
18-04-09  V.Ivanchenko (test55-V09-02-00)
- First version
